dc_title_s: Map of the state of North Dakota
dc_description_s: Shows county seats, townships, towns, roads and trails, railroads, water features, Indian reservations, and areas containing coal.; At head of title: Department of the Interior, General Land Office, William A. Richards, Commissioner.; Dec. 19 1906 and S Doc 194 59 2-- lower right margin.|33 x 43 Centimeters, on sheet 38 x 46|Scale 1:1,520,640. 1 inch equals 24 miles|General Map Collection
